The '''Boonta Speeder Race''' was an annual [[Landspeeder/Legends|speeder]] race that took place on the planet [[Boonta/Legends|Boonta]] two days after the [[Boonta Eve Classic/Legends|Boonta Eve Classic]] [[Podracing/Legends|podrace]] on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. It was established by [[Yenchara]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] of the [[Desilijic/Legends|Desilijic]] [[Kajidic/Legends|''kajidic'']] as a way of increasing profits by providing an alternative to the podrace in which [[Human/Legends|Humans]] could participate.<ref name="This is Podracing">{{SW|url=news/this-is-podracing-sports-in-the-star-wars-galaxy-part-1|series=Sports in the Star Wars Galaxy|text=Part 1: This Is Podracing|nolive=1}}</ref>

[[File:BoontaRace_2.jpg|thumb|left|Racing fans watch from the general spectators area.]]
The race track was a large, winding oval tunnel about sixteen kilometers long. In addition to the general spectators area, there were several enclosed viewing areas, featuring large viewing screens, set aside for more important spectators. In [[15 BBY/Legends|15 BBY]], [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Terrinald Screed/Legends|Screed]] watched the race from one of these private boxes.

That same year, the race was won by the team of [[Thall Joben/Legends|Thall Joben]], [[Jord Dusat]] and [[Kea Moll]] despite the interference of the [[Fromm Gang/Legends|Fromm Gang]] and [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] who had been hired by [[Sise Fromm]] to kill the young racers.

Boba Fett's droid, [[BL-17]], had previously tried to lure them into a trap by befriending [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] but was exposed and stopped by [[Proto One]] and [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]]. Joben entered the race but was pursued by Fett in ''[[Silver Speeder]]''. Fett tried to kill Joben, luring ''[[White Witch]]'' closer with a magnetic weapon. However, Fett was unaware that [[Tig Fromm]] had planted a [[Thermal detonator/Legends|thermal detonator]] on ''White Witch'' which was set to explode at the end of the race. Unfortunately for Fett, the weapon attracted not the ''Witch'', but the thermal detonator, destroying Fett's speeder and almost killing Fett. Frustrated, Fett captured Sise Fromm, [[Vlix Oncard]], and [[Tig Fromm]] on Boonta and turned them over to [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]].

[[File:BoontaRace_3.jpg|thumb|right|Thall Joben and Jord Dusat celebrate after winning the Boonta Speeder Race.]]
After the race, Dusat, Moll, and Joben were hired as speeder designers for the [[Zebulon Dak Speeder Corporation/Legends|Zebulon Dak Speeder Corporation]] by [[Zebulon Dak/Legends|Zebulon Dak]] himself. R2-D2 and C-3PO, not wanting to get in the way of this career opportunity, jettisoned themselves from the planet in an escape pod.

